Write a python program to display the sentence B after defining the variable A as shown in the following.?

A = (‘sister’,’USA’)

B = I have a sister and she stays at USA with her husband
----------------------------------------------------------------
A = ('sister', 'USA')
B = f" I have a {A[0]} and she stays at {A[1]} with her husband"
print(B)

